snippet.title: [Kingdom Rush Vengeance] The Pirate Kings Campaign is here!
snippet.description:
General, the time has come to show those so-called "Pirate Kings" who truly rules these waters! Get the Pirate Kings Campaign and bring them my Vengeance once and for all: 📱Google Play https://bit.ly/PK_PLAY 📱 App Store https://apple.co/3B1ZDAo 💻 Steam https://bit.ly/PK_STEAM 📱 Apple Arcade https://apple.co/3Zj27V2

The Pirate Kings DLC includes:

🦜 5 Epic New Stages
☠️ 10+ New Enemies
⚓ 4 Minibosses and 1 Boss
⛵ New Hero and Tower
👑 New Achievements
🏴 Easter Eggs Galore!

https://www.kingdomrushvengeance.com/piratekings

Don’t forget to like and subscribe, or ye might be walkin' the plank!

Join the Discord crew: https://discord.gg/ABkzxVTZ
